[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":186},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fother\u002F20211119\u002F2979001288\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fother\u002F20211119\u002F2979001288\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fother\u002F20211119\u002F2979001288\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fother\u002F20211119\u002F2979001288\u002F":161,"related:\u002Fother\u002F20211119\u002F2979001288\u002F":170},"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2021\u002F11\u002F19\u002Fset-heroku-server-timezone\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":139,"date":140,"description":18,"extension":141,"lang":142,"meta":143,"navigation":144,"path":145,"readingMinutes":146,"seo":147,"standalone":148,"stem":149,"tags":150,"tldr":158,"updated":158,"url":159,"__hash__":160},"content\u002F雜談\u002FHeroku-Server-TimeZone-時區設置.md","Heroku Server TimeZone 時區設置","2979001288",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":133},"minimark",[11,15,19,22,25,32,35,51,56,66,71,74,79,82,98,109,112,129],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"因為有一些較小的專案會需要顯示正確的時區，但是預設 Heroku 在時區設置上通常都不太正確，所以紀錄一下如何解決。",[12,20,21],{"id":21},"時區設置",[16,23,24],{},"因為長期一直使用 Heroku 做為專案開發的伺服器，但是某些專案是必須要看到正確的主機時間，所以如果沒有特別設置的話，Heroku 時間會以 GMT+0000(Coordinated Universal Time) 為主，所以在輸出時間時，就會是主機當地的時間",[16,26,27],{},[28,29],"img",{"alt":30,"src":31},"Coordinated Universal Time","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202021-11-19%2009.25.16.png",[16,33,34],{},"那麼這個解決方法很簡單，就是直接針對 Heroku 設定環境變數告知 Heroku 我要哪一個時區的時間就好了。",[16,36,37,38,42,43,46,47,50],{},"首先一開始請先打開 Heroku Settings 頁面，然後找到 ",[39,40,41],"code",{},"Config Vars"," 之後旁邊有一個按鈕是 ",[39,44,45],{},"Reveal Config Vars","，這邊是你設定 Heroku 環境變數 (",[39,48,49],{},".env",") 的地方",[16,52,53],{},[28,54],{"alt":45,"src":55},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202111190920.png",[16,57,58,59,62,63],{},"點一下它之後在 Key 的欄位 ",[39,60,61],{},"TZ"," 然後 Value 則是 ",[39,64,65],{},"Asia\u002FTaipei",[16,67,68],{},[28,69],{"alt":21,"src":70},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202021-11-19%2009.23.47.png",[16,72,73],{},"輸入完畢之後按下儲存，並重新啟動 Heroku 就可以看到時區正常囉~",[16,75,76],{},[28,77],{"alt":65,"src":78},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202021-11-19%2009.25.09.png",[16,80,81],{},"當然你也可以透過終端機登入 Heroku 使用指令的方式添加",[83,84,89],"pre",{"className":85,"code":86,"language":87,"meta":88,"style":88},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","heroku config:add TZ=\"Asia\u002FTaipei\"\n","cmd","",[39,90,91],{"__ignoreMap":88},[92,93,96],"span",{"class":94,"line":95},"line",1,[92,97,86],{},[16,99,100,101,108],{},"如果不知道時區名稱的話也可以參考 ",[102,103,107],"a",{"href":104,"rel":105},"https:\u002F\u002Fen.wikipedia.org\u002Fwiki\u002FList_of_tz_database_time_zones",[106],"nofollow","Wiki","。",[12,110,111],{"id":111},"參考文獻",[113,114,115,123],"ul",{},[116,117,118],"li",{},[102,119,122],{"href":120,"rel":121},"https:\u002F\u002Fstackoverflow.com\u002Fquestions\u002F14479970\u002Fheroku-server-timezone-and-logs-time",[106],"Heroku Server timezone and logs time",[116,124,125],{},[102,126,128],{"href":104,"rel":127},[106],"List of tz database time zones",[130,131,132],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}",{"title":88,"searchDepth":134,"depth":134,"links":135},2,[136,137,138],{"id":14,"depth":134,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":134,"text":21},{"id":111,"depth":134,"text":111},"雜談","2021-11-19 09:16:32","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fheroku-server-timezone","1",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"雜談\u002FHeroku-